<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id7807e231-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s460rrr–8"><num value="460rrr–8">§ 460rrr–8.</num><heading> Termination of Commission</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Commission shall terminate on the date that is 10 years after <date date="2006-10-12">October 12, 2006</date>.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id7807e232-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/109/337/s10">Pub. L. 109–337, § 10</ref>, <date date="2006-10-12">Oct. 12, 2006</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/120/1782">120 Stat. 1782</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
